body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:

Oscar C. Nysted to Archie T. Anrich: Morgan Street and 74th Street. Price, $2,700.
Kristian Lundstrom to Fred T. Nelson: Peoria Street and Garfield Boulevard. Price, $8.
